  "title": "Recruitment Consultant (Foreign Worker/Earn up to $10k)",
  "description": "<p>To acquire new corporate clients in Singapore and promote People360’s foreign manpower recruitment solutions through B2B canvassing, prospecting, meetings, and relationship building.<br /><br />We recruit regional foreign workers from China, Malaysia, Thailand, Philippines, India, Myanmar, Vietnam, Sri Lanka, and Indonesia for businesses in Singapore.<br /><br /><u><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></u></p><p><ul><li>Conduct <strong>outdoor canvassing and walk-in visits</strong> to target industrial sectors (services, manufacturing, logistics, construction)</li><li>Identify manpower needs and secure job orders</li><li>Cold call, email, and follow up with prospects</li><li>Build and maintain a sales pipeline via CRM</li><li>Work closely with the recruitment delivery team on placements</li><li>Manage client relationships post-placement for repeat business</li><li>Coordinate with overseas suppliers to shortlist and interview foreign applicants</li><li>Coordinate final interview with clients via online and face-to-face methods</li><li>Coordinate with admin & operations department for visa application and onboarding formalities</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><p><p>- Strong communication & persuasion skills<br />- Confident, resilient, and sales-driven<br />- Able to work independently and self motivated<br />- Experience in recruitment/manpower /telemarketing or outdoor/field sales<br />- Comfortable with outdoor prospecting & cold approach<br />- Proven track record of sales experience</p><p><u><strong>Remuneration & Package</strong></u></p><p>- Basic Salary: S$1600 - S$1800 & Earn up to $10,000 - $15,000 Monthly with Sales Commission. No cap on earnings<br />- Commission Scale: 20% - 35% Tier Scale (Monthly Payout)<br /><br /><strong>Commission Illustration (Example)</strong></p><p>Monthly Net Sales Profit: $22,000<br />Commission (30%): $6,600<br />Basic Salary: $1,600<br /><strong>Total Monthly Earnings: $8,200</strong><br /><br />- Annual leave 14 days per year<br />- Transport Claims (Taxi or Petrol)<br />- 5-day office hours </p></p></p>",
